# 1. reading specific number of bytes from the file 
with open("text.txt","r") as f1:
    read_data = f1.read(7)
    print(read_data)


_______________________________________________________________________
output
ChatGPT
_______________________________________________________________________


# 2. reading all the content from the file 
with open("text.txt","r") as f1:
    read_data = f1.read()
    print(read_data)


_______________________________________________________________________
output
ChatGPT was created by OpenAI, an AI and research company. 
The company launched ChatGPT on November 30, 2022.
ChatGPT is a natural language processing tool driven by AI technology.
_______________________________________________________________________



# 3. reading the file using for loop
with open("text.txt","r") as f1:
    for i in f1:
        print (i)
_______________________________________________________________________
output
ChatGPT was created by OpenAI, an AI and research company. 

The company launched ChatGPT on November 30, 2022.

ChatGPT is a natural language processing tool driven by AI technology.
_______________________________________________________________________




# 4. reading lines using readline()
with open("text.txt","r") as f1:
    read_data = f1.readline()
    read_data1 = f1.readline() # to read another line
    print(read_data)
    print(read_data1)
_______________________________________________________________________
output
ChatGPT was created by OpenAI, an AI and research company. 

The company launched ChatGPT on November 30, 2022.
_______________________________________________________________________



# 5. reading lines using readlines()
with open("text.txt","r") as f1:
    read_data = f1.readlines()
    print(read_data)
    
_______________________________________________________________________
output
['ChatGPT was created by OpenAI, an AI and research company. \n', 
'The company launched ChatGPT on November 30, 2022.\n', 
'ChatGPT is a natural language processing tool driven by AI technology.']
_______________________________________________________________________
